{
  "stem": "107.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had just to leave it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They produced underwear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very successful factory when there was a cold winter, which isn't always.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it went up and down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, he was a rather gifted man and knew  he had to start from the beginning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he went back to school and became a-- accountant-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] public accountant, and started a practice, and supported his family.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "While he was in school, my mother started a boutique with handicrafts that partially was done by her and by a couple of other women who she employed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somehow, we got through the times that he did not really make any money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had no savings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was after the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the beginning was hard but very comfortable for me as a child.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't know much about hardship.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, my parents had a very good marriage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very comfortable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was never any kind of screaming or yelling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was first and only child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I was six-- no, when I was five, my sister was born, who was a lovely little baby.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there no great problems.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The city was a city of-- and I can't even tell.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Today it seems so little.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were 30,000 or 35,000 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And yet we had culture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had a theatre and an opera and, and music.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It is hard to believe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were about 3,000 Jews, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] most of them doing quite well, except for newcomers, who, after first war, came with nothing, from the east, usually, most from Russia or Poland, and started from the beginning, and were somehow supported and made it.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nobody ever starved in the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
